  "title": "Configure the tenant setting for OO",
  "content": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\">\n<p>After you have deployed and enabled the Operations Orchestration capability for a tenant, the tenant admin needs to set up Operations Orchestration Containerized (OO Containerized) before users can use it. The setup procedure includes enabling a tenant setting in Application Settings. </p>\n<div class=\"transcontent stn-begin--OOMenuVisibility\"> </div>\n<h2>Enable the tenant setting</h2>\n<ol>\n<li>Log in to the SMAX agent interface as the tenant admin. </li>\n<li>In the agent interface, navigate to <strong>Administration</strong> &gt; <strong>Configuration</strong> &gt; <strong>Application Settings</strong>. </li>\n<li>Make sure that the <strong>Enable Operations Orchestration</strong> setting is set to <strong>On</strong>. By default, this setting is <strong>On</strong>. </li>\n</ol>\n<p>This tenant setting controls the availability of the following UI items (which are available only when the tenant setting is On): </p>\n<ul>\n<li>The following option under Administration: <strong>Orchestration Settings<br/>\n<a class=\"image\" href=\"https://staging.docs.microfocus.com/file/images/3/38/ESM202111_MTOO_new_menu_admin_2.jpeg\" title=\"https://staging.docs.microfocus.com/file/images/3/38/ESM202111_MTOO_new_menu_admin_2.jpeg\"> <img alt=\"\" border=\"0\" file=\"https://staging.docs.microfocus.com/mediawiki/images/3/38/ESM202111_MTOO_new_menu_admin_2.jpeg\" height=\"426\" hspace=\"0\" src=\"../../../images/ESM202111_MTOO_new_menu_admin_2_221f7a3f.jpeg\" vspace=\"0\" width=\"800\"/> </a> </strong></li>\n<li>The following menu item under <strong>RUN</strong>: <strong>Automation Operations<br/>\n<a class=\"image\" href=\"https://staging.docs.microfocus.com/file/images/3/32/ESM202111_MTOO_new_menu_run_new1.png\" title=\"https://staging.docs.microfocus.com/file/images/3/32/ESM202111_MTOO_new_menu_run_new1.png\"> <img alt=\"\" border=\"0\" file=\"https://staging.docs.microfocus.com/mediawiki/images/3/32/ESM202111_MTOO_new_menu_run_new1.png\" height=\"388\" hspace=\"0\" src=\"../../../images/ESM202111_MTOO_new_menu_run_new1_cbe861b0.png\" style=\"width: 800px; height: 388px; margin: 0px; border: 0px solid black;\" vspace=\"0\" width=\"800\"/> </a> </strong></li>\n<li>The following role permission under <strong>Administration </strong>&gt; <strong>People </strong>&gt; <strong>Roles</strong>: <strong>Permission to manage Operations Orchestration<br/>\n<a class=\"image\" href=\"/file/images/8/81/ESM202111_MTOO_permission.png\" title=\"/file/images/8/81/ESM202111_MTOO_permission.png\"> <img alt=\"\" border=\"0\" file=\"/mediawiki/images/8/81/ESM202111_MTOO_permission.png\" height=\"165\" hspace=\"0\" src=\"../../../images/ESM202111_MTOO_permission_e6ef2a14.png\" style=\"width:509px;height:165px;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;margin-left:0px;margin-right:0px;border:0px solid black;\" vspace=\"0\" width=\"509\"/> </a> </strong></li>\n<li>The following endpoint type under <strong>Administration </strong>&gt; <strong>Utilities </strong>&gt; <strong>Integration </strong>&gt; <strong>Endpoints </strong>&gt; <strong>Add </strong>&gt; <strong>Endpoint type</strong>: <strong>Operations Orchestration Containerized</strong><br/>\n<a class=\"image\" href=\"https://staging.docs.microfocus.com/file/images/a/a2/Endpoints_type.png\" title=\"https://staging.docs.microfocus.com/file/images/a/a2/Endpoints_type.png\"> <img alt=\"\" border=\"0\" file=\"https://staging.docs.microfocus.com/mediawiki/images/a/a2/Endpoints_type.png\" height=\"367\" hspace=\"0\" src=\"../../../images/Endpoints_type_7edc7e56.png\" style=\"width: 800px; height: 367px; margin: 0px; border: 0px solid black;\" vspace=\"0\" width=\"800\"/> </a></li>\n</ul>\n<p>Note that the tenant setting doesn't control the visibility of the following item on the Role form (which is always available):</p>\n<ul>\n<li>The <strong>Orchestration Settings</strong> option in the <strong>Administration menu visibility</strong> section:<br/>\n<a class=\"image\" href=\"/file/images/9/9a/ESM202111_MTOO_menu_visibility_orchestration_settings.png\" title=\"/file/images/9/9a/ESM202111_MTOO_menu_visibility_orchestration_settings.png\"> <img alt=\"\" border=\"0\" file=\"/mediawiki/images/9/9a/ESM202111_MTOO_menu_visibility_orchestration_settings.png\" height=\"306\" hspace=\"0\" src=\"../../../images/ESM202111_MTOO_menu_visibility_orchestration_settings_6ac63279.png\" style=\"width: 700px; height: 306px; margin: 0px; border: 0px solid black;\" vspace=\"0\" width=\"700\"/> </a></li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"transcontent stn-end--OOMenuVisibility\"> </div>\n</div>",
